## Project structure

```
src/openfugu/
├── api/          # FastAPI OpenAI-compatible server
├── router/       # Fugu fast path (Qwen3-0.6B + selection head)
├── conductor/    # Fugu-Ultra (workflow DSL + executor)
├── workers/      # LiteLLM worker pool
├── training/     # SFT, sep-CMA-ES, GRPO
└── harness/      # Tool loop, coding harness
```

## Development

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pytest tests/ -v
ruff check src tests
```

## Comparison

| | Sakana Fugu | OpenFugu |
|---|-------------|----------|
| Source | Closed | Open (Apache-2.0) |
| Self-host | ❌ | ✅ |
| Training | ❌ | ✅ SFT + CMA-ES + GRPO |
| Transparency | Black box | Full routing metadata |
| Cost | $5-30/M + subscription | Free + your API costs |

Full comparison: [docs/COMPARISON.md](docs/COMPARISON.md)

